node.title: Three community COVID-19 cases detected in Queensland border town
node.alt: Premier in red jacket with black top, brown hair and earrings speaking in front of green trees and buildings
node.description: Queensland records three new locally acquired cases of COVID-19 in Goondiwindi as the mayor of the southern border town says he is concerned about gatherings in northern New South Wales.
node.content:
["Queensland has recorded three new locally acquired cases of COVID-19 in Goondiwindi as the mayor of the\u00a0southern border town says he is concerned about gatherings\u00a0in northern New South Wales.", "Premier Annastacia Palaszczuk said one of the latest cases was an unvaccinated contact of a known cluster and was not of concern.", "Another case was also unvaccinated and had been\u00a0in the community for five days but\u00a0all of their household contacts have tested negative.", "The third new case was a woman in her 30s who has been in the community for four days and had one dose of the AstraZeneca vaccine.", "Ms Palaszczuk said the\u00a0cases show why it is so important to get vaccinated.", "Ms Palaszczuk said Goondiwindi, which has a first dose rate of 93.1 per cent, was a \"highly vaccinated community\".", "
Interstate parties concern mayor
", "Queensland Health said it was\u00a0investigating whether a case reported late yesterday was connected to a\u00a0truck driver who spent time in the town on the weekend, before later testing positive while in New South Wales.", "But the Goondiwindi Regional Council Mayor Lawrence Springborg suggested that was not the case.", "Mr\u00a0Springborg told\u00a0ABC Brisbane \"from the information I have\", the positive COVID case was acquired interstate.", "\"This was not acquired in our town,\" he said.", "\"It was most likely acquired at one of the significant number of gatherings over the border in Moree last week and over last weekend.", "\"Of course that's a real concern for us because my information speaking to my colleagues across the border is that there is a very significant growing number of cases relating to those gatherings last week, of which I understand that there was a very large proportion of unvaccinated people.\"", "More to come.", "", "
Outbreak: How Australia lost control of the Delta variant
"]
